## Installation
This repository is tested on üêçPython 3.7+ and üî•PyTorch 1.8.2+, as well as it works fine on macOS, Windows, Linux.
```bash
pip install VFastPunct
```

## Run
```python
>>> from vfastpunct import VFastPunct
>>> punct = VFastPunct(model_name='mBertPuncCap', no_cuda=False)
>>> punct('vi·ªát nam qu·ªëc hi·ªáu ch√≠nh th·ª©c l√† c·ªông h√≤a x√£ h·ªôi ch·ªß nghƒ©a vi·ªát nam l√† m·ªôt qu·ªëc gia n·∫±m ·ªü c·ª±c ƒë√¥ng c·ªßa b√°n ƒë·∫£o ƒë√¥ng d∆∞∆°ng thu·ªôc khu v·ª±c ƒë√¥ng nam √° gi√°p v·ªõi l√†o campuchia trung qu·ªëc bi·ªÉn ƒë√¥ng v√† v·ªãnh th√°i lan')
'Vi·ªát Nam qu·ªëc hi·ªáu ch√≠nh th·ª©c l√† C·ªông h√≤a X√£ h·ªôi ch·ªß nghƒ©a Vi·ªát Nam, l√† m·ªôt qu·ªëc gia n·∫±m ·ªü c·ª±c ƒê√¥ng c·ªßa b√°n ƒë·∫£o ƒê√¥ng D∆∞∆°ng, thu·ªôc khu v·ª±c ƒê√¥ng Nam √Å, gi√°p v·ªõi L√†o, Campuchia, Trung Qu·ªëc, Bi·ªÉn ƒê√¥ng v√† V·ªãnh Th√°i Lan.'
